data.description:
This beautiful 5 bedroom home has almost 2700 SF and has 3 1/2 bathrooms with the primary bedroom downstairs and a large family room upstairs. Available for 6-12 month lease. The home features a large open kitchen, solar panels, and a covered patio with a fenced back yard. Washer, dryer and refrigerator included. Pets allowed but restricted to downstairs. Located in the desirable Risposa Vita community, it is conveniently located close to schools, shopping, Loop 410, I-10, Ft Sam Houston and JBSA Randolph.

Pets allowed with restrictions and limited to downstairs. Tenant to pay an additional $35 monthly fee to cover AC filters and the tenant portal.
